{
  "stem": "11722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They pulled out my tooth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I volunteered on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Every other Sunday we had off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I volunteered-- to get out of the camp-- to clean the SS barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was very dangerous to volunteer for anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "You never knew what was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was awaiting you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Anyone who tried to escape-- there was a escape attempt one time at Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But the group, they tried to dig a tunnel under the fence, and they were caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Everyone in the group was hung to teach us a lesson-- that's what will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] And-- and then one day, in 1945, I think-- it was in January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a cold night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was snowing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They woke-- they awakened us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We had to line up and put our-- our clothes on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Our clothes consisted of-- of a-- of a shirt made out of some kind of a cotton fabric, with no collar; a pajama cotton jacket with a cotton pajama pants; a piece of cloth for socks; [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shoes that were canvas top with wooden soles.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "The soles must've been an inch thick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had caps, cotton caps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We had a cotton coat, like a robe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "We had to line up in the cold of the winter, and they were evacuating the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I guess the Russians started an invasion, and the Nazis didn't want to leave anybody behind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "They were evacuating all camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "They were burning the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "But all those sick who couldn't march, they didn't want any witnesses to tell the world of these atrocities that took place.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
